snippet.title: Daymare 1994: Sandcastle - Exclusive Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the cinematic reveal trailer for Daymare 1994: Sandcastle, the sequel to the Resident Evil 2-inspired Daymare 1998. Daymare 1994 is due out in 2022 for both PC and consoles.

#IGN #Daymare1994
